OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FFormer detective Maggie Oliver spoke
OL,8,Fto Good Morning Britain ahead of the
OL,9,FHigh Court Hearing.
OL,11,FA foundation set up by a former
OL,12,Fdetective-turned-whistleblower has
OL,13,Ftold the High Court that the
OL,14,FGovernment has "effectively allowed
OL,15,Fthe abuse" of thousands of children by
OL,16,Fnot acting fast enough on child sexual
OL,17,Fexploitation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
