PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe Maggie Oliver Foundation is hoping
OL,8,Fto take legal action against the Home
OL,9,FOffice over its alleged failure to
OL,10,Fadopt 17 recommendations suggested by
OL,11,Fan Independent Inquiry into Child
OL,12,FSexual Abuse (IICSA).
OL,14,FThe foundation was set up by former
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police detective
OL,16,FMaggie Oliver after she became a
OL,17,Fwhistleblower about the force's
OL,18,Finaction over grooming gangs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FTo take legal action, the Foundation
OL,8,Fwill first have to prove the case is
OL,9,F"arguable", something the Government
OL,10,Fis denying.
OL,12,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain,
OL,13,FMaggie Oliver said: "I hope they will
OL,14,Fgive us leave to take this to a full
OL,15,Fjudicial review... and then we can
OL,16,Fargue the case for why these 20
OL,17,Frecommendations should be implemented.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"And if they're not the country will
OL,8,Fknow they're not, and so I hope people
OL,9,Fpower and victims and survivors will
OL,10,Fchallenge and shout out about how
OL,11,Funacceptable this is."
OL,13,FConcluding in 2022, the inquiry lasted
OL,14,Fseven years at a cost of #200 million.
OL,15,FIt was launched to examine how public
OL,16,Fand private institutions failed to
OL,17,Fprotect children from sexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FChristopher Jacobs, for the
OL,8,Ffoundation, told the court 17 of the
OL,9,F20 recommendations had not been
OL,10,Fimplemented as of July 8, 2025.
OL,12,FThe claim centres on three
OL,13,Frecommendations which the Maggie
OL,14,FOliver Foundation say the Government
OL,15,Fis failing to implement, which
OL,16,Fincludes recording the age, ethnicity,
OL,17,Freligion, and occupation of
OL,18,Fperpetrators of child sexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe other recommendations the
OL,8,Ffoundation argues are not being
OL,9,Fimplemented are ending the use of pain-
OL,10,Finducing restraint on children in
OL,11,Fcustody, and ensuring those in care
OL,12,Fhave greater access to justice.
OL,14,FMr Jacobs said around 500,000 children
OL,15,Fare sexually abused every year and
OL,16,Fthat the Government has "effectively
OL,17,Fallowed the abuse to continue" by
OL,18,Ftaking an "inconsistent and arbitrary
OL,19,Fapproach" to the recommendations.
OL,26,@xD@YOUyD@^O]zD@KOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FIn written submissions, he said: "The
OL,8,Fclaimant maintains that the
OL,9,Fobfuscations, denials and delays by
OL,10,Fsuccessive Governments in implementing
OL,11,Fthe thorough and extensively reasoned
OL,12,Frecommendations of the seven-year
OL,13,Finquiry must have contributed to
OL,14,Fthousands of otherwise preventable
OL,15,Fcases of sexual abuse and exploitation
OL,16,Fof children over the last three and a
OL,17,Fhalf years."
OL,26,@oD@bOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FMr Jacobs also said the Government is
OL,8,Ffailing to set a timetable for when
OL,9,Fthese recommendations will be
OL,10,Fimplemented.
OL,12,FHe added: "The failure by successive
OL,13,FGovernments to respond to the ongoing
OL,14,Fthreat of child sexual abuse and child
OL,15,Fsexual exploitation is a matter of
OL,16,Fnational importance and urgency."
OL,18,FJack Anderson, for the Home Office,
OL,19,Fsaid in written submissions that the
OL,20,Fclaim is "not arguable".
OL,26,@tD@KOUxD@aO]|D@JOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FHe said: "The Government is not
OL,8,Fobliged to implement the
OL,9,Frecommendations of IICSA, they are
OL,10,Frecommendations, but no more than
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FThe barrister also said the Home
OL,14,FSecretary had "accepted in full" the
OL,15,Ffour recommendations that relate to
OL,16,Fher department, while the statement
OL,17,Ffrom the previous Home Secretary "is
OL,18,Fnot a clear, precise and unambiguous
OL,19,Frepresentation that the
OL,20,Frecommendations of the IICSA will be
OL,21,Fimplemented".
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@FO]vD@OOUvD@`O]yD@bOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772787895
OL,3,CGovernment 'effectively allowed abuse'
OL,4,Cof children, former detective tells
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FIn relation to setting a timetable, Mr
OL,8,FAnderson said the Government "wants to
OL,9,Fget policy right and that takes time".
OL,11,FHe added: "The Government has
OL,12,Findicated the steps it is taking, but
OL,13,Fnot all of them can be assigned a
OL,14,Fdefinite end-date having regard to the
OL,15,Fdesirability of consulting
OL,16,Fstakeholders, the policy work required
OL,17,Fand the myriad pressures on public
OL,18,Fbusiness."
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@eO]sD@KOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
